# Day-of-Week Effect in Indian Power Sector

This repository contains the full research pipeline for investigating the Day-of-Week effect in Indian power sector equities.

## Reproducibility Instructions

### 1. Setup Environment
```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Run Phases
Run the phases sequentially:
```bash
python scripts/run_phase1.py
python scripts/run_phase2.py
python scripts/run_phase3.py
python scripts/run_phase4.py
python scripts/run_phase5.py
```

Check `outputs/reports/` for generated reports.
